  "texts": [
    "Our benchmark includes two test sets: SeaRefuse-G and SeaRefuse-H.",
    "The unanswerable questions in SeaRefuse-G are generated by GPT-4o while the unanswerable questions in SeaRefuse-H are written by humans.",
    "In evaluation, we report the F1-score of each model on correctly refusing questions about non-existing entities.",
    "We adopt a keyword-matching approach to detect refusal responses.",
    "Further details of the dataset and evaluation settings are in Appendix B.3."
  ],
